    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA332-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">1. itu piriviṭai melinta talaimakaḷait tōḻi kaḷavu kālattu vaṟpuṟuttatu (EN, ER, ET, EV: vaṟpuṟuppa talaivi kūṟiyatu). 2. vaṉpoṟai (ER, EV: vaṉpuṟai) etirmaṟuttatūumām.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">1. This is how in the time of secrecy the confidante encouraged HER who had become weak in the time of separation. 2. It is also being desolate in the face of encouragement.</p>
        </div>
      <div xml:id="NA332">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>ikuḷait tōḻiyiḵ teṉṉeṉap paṭumō</l>
<l>kuvaḷai kuṟunar nīrvēṭ ṭāṅku</l>
<l>nāḷu nāḷuṭaṉ kalavun tōḷē</l>
<l>toṉṉilai vaḻīiyaniṉ ṟoṭiyeṉap paṉmā</l>
<l>ṇuraitta lāṉṟici ṉīyē viṭarmukai</l>
<l>yīṉpiṇa voṭukkiya viruṅkōḷ vayappuli</l>
<l>yirainacaiip parikku malaimutaṟ ciṟuneṟi</l>
<l>talainā ḷaṉṉa pēṇalaṉ palanā</l>
<l>ḷāriruḷ varutal kāṇpēṟ</l>
<l>kiyāṅkā kummē yilaṅkiḻai ceṟippē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Comrade, friend, what is to be said of this?</l>
<l>Leave off, you, telling many times:</l>
<l rend="indent2">*[Your] shoulder that is blended together [with his] day by day,</l>
<l rend="indent3">as if those plucking waterlilies wanted water!</l>
<l rend="indent2">[Yet] your bracelets that have slipped from the old state!*</l>
<l>How can there be tightness of [my] shining jewels,</l>
<l rend="indent">for me who see [him] coming in difficult darkness</l>
<l rend="indent2">many days, the one who does not care, like the first day,</l>
<l rend="indent3">across the small path at the mountain base, where the big tiger</l>
<l rend="indent4">strong in killing runs yearning for prey, controlled by [its] 	</l>
<l rend="indent4">female giving birth in a clefted cave?</l>
      </lg>
      </div>
